This package bundles third-party source files:

- src/blast.c
- src/blast.h

These files are from zlib contrib/blast and are authored by Mark Adler.
They are distributed under the zlib license.

The bundled blast code is used to decompress PKWare Data Compression Library
(DCL) streams, which are used by DATASUS DBC files.

See the original notices preserved in the bundled source files.
